var TEAMS=[{name:'Kinetix Deuces Wild',detail:'Kiss My Ace opponent'},{name:'Unmatchables',detail:'Kiss My Ace opponent'},{name:'Tennis Addiction',detail:'Kiss My Ace opponent'},{name:'Love Hurts',detail:'Kiss My Ace opponent'},{name:'IKST Gulph Mills',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Saint Albans Swim & Tennis',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'UD Smash Squad',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Simply Smashing',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Merion Cricket 18+',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Philly Cricket',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Quad Squad',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'},{name:'Kicking Aces',detail:'Pour Decisions opponent'}];
function toggleDropdown(tab){if('ontouchstart' in window){document.querySelectorAll('.team-tab').forEach(t=>{if(t!==tab)t.classList.remove('dropdown-open');});tab.classList.toggle('dropdown-open');}}
document.addEventListener('click',function(e){if(!e.target.closest('.team-tab')){document.querySelectorAll('.team-tab').forEach(t=>t.classList.remove('dropdown-open'));}});
function switchTeam(team,btn){
  // Close dropdowns
  document.querySelectorAll('.team-tab').forEach(t=>t.classList.remove('dropdown-open'));
  // Highlight the dropdown item
  document.querySelectorAll('.league-dropdown a').forEach(a=>a.classList.remove('dd-active'));
  if(btn&&btn.classList)btn.classList.add('dd-active');
  // Highlight parent tab
  document.querySelectorAll('.team-tab').forEach(t=>t.classList.remove('active'));
  var parentTab=btn.closest?btn.closest('.team-tab'):null;
  if(parentTab)parentTab.classList.add('active');
  // Switch panel
  document.querySelectorAll('.team-panel').forEach(p=>p.classList.remove('active'));
  var panel=document.getElementById('panel-'+team);
  if(panel)panel.classList.add('active');
  currentTeam=team;
  document.querySelectorAll('.dnav-btn,.bnav-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));
  document.querySelectorAll('.dnav-btn')[0].classList.add('active');
  document.getElementById('mob-schedule').classList.add('active');
  showPage(team,'schedule');currentPage='schedule';window.scrollTo(0,0);
}
function switchPage(page,btn){document.querySelectorAll('.dnav-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));document.querySelectorAll('.bnav-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));btn.classList.add('active');var pages=['schedule','docket','standings','roster','whatsapp'];var idx=pages.indexOf(page);if(idx>=0){if(btn.classList.contains('dnav-btn'))document.getElementById('mob-'+page).classList.add('active');else document.querySelectorAll('.dnav-btn')[idx].classList.add('active');}showPage(currentTeam,page);currentPage=page;window.scrollTo(0,0);}
function showPage(team,page){document.getElementById('panel-'+team).querySelectorAll('.page-view').forEach(v=>v.classList.remove('active'));var t=document.getElementById(team+'-'+page);if(t)t.classList.add('active');}
function openProfile(name,initials,colorClass,detail,bio,ntrp,role){var av=document.getElementById('modal-av');av.className='modal-av '+colorClass;av.textContent=initials.replace(/[0-9]/g,'');if(photoData[initials])av.innerHTML='<img src="'+photoData[initials]+'">';document.getElementById('modal-name').textContent=name;document.getElementById('modal-detail').textContent=detail;document.getElementById('modal-ntrp').textContent=ntrp;var bioEl=document.getElementById('modal-bio');var bioSec=document.getElementById('bio-sec');if(bio){bioEl.textContent=bio;bioSec.style.display='block';}else bioSec.style.display='none';document.getElementById('modal-cap-badge').innerHTML=role==='Captain'?'<span class="modal-cap">👑 Captain</span>':'';currentProfile=initials;document.getElementById('profileModal').classList.add('open');document.body.style.overflow='hidden';}
function closeProfile(e){if(e&&e.target!==document.getElementById('profileModal'))return;document.getElementById('profileModal').classList.remove('open');document.body.style.overflow='';currentProfile=null;}
function handlePhoto(event){var file=event.target.files[0];if(!file||!currentProfile)return;var reader=new FileReader();reader.onload=function(e){photoData[currentProfile]=e.target.result;document.getElementById('modal-av').innerHTML='<img src="'+e.target.result+'">';var c=document.getElementById('av-'+currentProfile);if(c)c.innerHTML='<img src="'+e.target.result+'">';};reader.readAsDataURL(file);}
function openSearch(){document.getElementById('searchOverlay').classList.add('open');setTimeout(()=>document.getElementById('searchField').focus(),100);doSearch('');}
function closeSearch(){document.getElementById('searchOverlay').classList.remove('open');document.getElementById('searchField').value='';}
function doSearch(q){var ql=q.toLowerCase();var pl=q?PLAYERS.filter(p=>p.name.toLowerCase().includes(ql)):PLAYERS;var tl=q?TEAMS.filter(t=>t.name.toLowerCase().includes(ql)):TEAMS;document.getElementById('playerResults').innerHTML=pl.map(p=>'<div class="s-item"><div class="s-av">'+p.init+'</div><div class="s-info"><div class="s-name">'+p.name+'</div><div class="s-sub">'+p.detail+'</div></div><span class="s-tag">Player</span></div>').join('')||'<div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);padding:12px 0;">No players found</div>';document.getElementById('teamResults').innerHTML=tl.map(t=>{var i=t.name.split(' ').map(w=>w[0]).join('').slice(0,2);return'<div class="s-item"><div class="s-av team">'+i+'</div><div class="s-info"><div class="s-name">'+t.name+'</div><div class="s-sub">'+t.detail+'</div></div><span class="s-tag">Team</span></div>';}).join('')||'<div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);padding:12px 0;">No teams found</div>';}
</script>
</body>
